            "https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/article/2024/jul/14/trump-rally-shooting-fbi-names-20-year-old-from-bethel-park-as-subject-involved"
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentence": "He attended Bethel Park High School",
          "refs": []
        },
        {
          "sentence": "He attempted to join the school's rifle club, participating in \"preseason\", but was such a bad shot he was considered \"dangerous\", being rejected from the team and asked not to come back",
          "refs": [
            "https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/article/2024/jul/15/trump-shooter-motive"
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentence": "He joined the National Technical Honor Society in 2021 while a junior in high school",
          "refs": [
            "https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/nation/2024/07/20/trump-assassination-attempt-updates-shooting-investigation/74483441007/",
            "https://slate.com/news-and-politics/2024/07/trump-shooter-gun-thomas-crooks-ar-15-expertise-military.html"
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentence": "In 2022, he graduated with high honors and won a $500 \"star award\" from the National Math and Science Initiative",
          "refs": [
            "https://www.telegraph.co.uk/us/news/2024/07/15/trump-shooter-rejected-school-rifle-club-dangerous-shot/"
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentence": "Classmates and school officials characterized him as being quiet; classmates said that he was often bullied for various reasons    including his quiet demeanor, body odor, as well as for wearing camouflage hunting outfits and surgical masks to school",
          "refs": [
            "[ERROR retrieving ref link]",
            "https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/investigations/2024/07/14/thomas-crooks-trump-rally-shooter/74397935007/",
            "https://triblive.com/local/awards-and-recognition-program-honors-bethel-park-graduates/"
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentence": "He earned an associate degree in engineering science from the Community College of Allegheny County in Pittsburgh, graduating two months before the shooting",
          "refs": []
        },
        {
          "sentence": "He was employed as a dietary aide in a nursing home at the time of the shooting",
          "refs": []
        },
        {
