      "section_title": "Attempted assassination of Donald Trump",
      "section_content": [
        {
          "sentence": "Prior to the shooting, Crooks searched for images and public appearances of Trump, President Joe Biden, Attorney General Merrick Garland, FBI Director Christopher A",
          "refs": []
        },
        {
          "sentence": "Wray, and Catherine, Princess of Wales,    as well as for information regarding the Republican National Convention  and the Democratic National Convention",
          "refs": [
            "https://abcnews.go.com/Politics/live-updates/donald-trump-rally-shooting-assassination-attempt/?id=111916828&entryId=111985581",
            "https://www.nytimes.com/2024/07/17/us/politics/secret-service-trump-shooting.html",
            "https://www.vanityfair.com/style/story/the-trump-shooter-searched-a-british-royal-prior-to-assassination-attempt-investigators-say",
            "https://www.npr.org/2024/07/14/nx-s1-5039185/who-was-trump-rally-shooter-thomas-matthew-crooks"
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentence": "He also searched the Internet for information on major depressive disorder and the Oxford High School shooting, with authorities finding an arrest photograph of Oxford shooter Ethan Crumbley on his phone",
          "refs": [
            "https://web.archive.org/web/20241207204617/https://www.reuters.com/world/us/fbi-says-trump-gunman-spent-months-looking-target-before-settling-trump-2024-08-28/"
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentence": "On July 6, the same day he registered for the rally, Crooks searched \"how far was Oswald from Kennedy\" in reference to former president John F",
          "refs": []
        },
        {
          "sentence": "Kennedy and the gunman who assassinated him",
          "refs": []
        },
        {
          "sentence": "Crooks also searched for information on power plants and the attempted assassination of Slovakian prime minister Robert Fico",
          "refs": [
            "https://www.cnn.com/2024/07/17/politics/thomas-matthew-crooks-trump-shooter/index.html"
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentence": "He used a number of aliases and encrypted communication accounts to buy firearm supplies and bomb-making material",
          "refs": []
        },
        {
          "sentence": "On July 12, 2024, Crooks went to a shooting range where he was a member to practice firing",
          "refs": [
            "https://apnews.com/article/fbi-trump-assassination-attempt-shooting-f1ff0a636f3e2e1a28762c400852167e"
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentence": "He purchased over 50 rounds of ammunition and a ladder before going to the rally on July 13",
          "refs": []
        },
        {
          "sentence": "He requested the day off from work because he had \"something important to do\", telling his co-workers that he would return the next day",
          "refs": [
            "https://www.cnn.com/2024/07/15/us/thomas-crooks-trump-rally-shooting-invs/index.html"
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentence": "Hours before the shooting, Crooks's parents had called the police to report him as missing and expressed concern about his wellbeing",
          "refs": [
            "https://abcnews.go.com/US/fbi-searches-motive-trump-assassination-attempt-cautions-investigation/story?id=111945201",
            "https://www.telegraph.co.uk/us/news/2024/07/15/trump-shooter-rejected-school-rifle-club-dangerous-shot/"
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentence": "On July 13, Crooks went to the Trump rally",
          "refs": [
            "https://www.ctvnews.ca/world/trump-shooter-requested-saturday-off-from-work-and-told-colleagues-he-d-be-back-at-work-sunday-officials-say-1.6967044"
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentence": "He climbed onto a building that was being used by police as a staging area",
          "refs": [
            "https://www.fox10phoenix.com/news/trump-shooters-parents-called-police-hours-before-assassination-attempt"
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentence": "Text messages from a police sniper indicate that the police were aware of him already 90 minutes before the shooting",
          "refs": [
            "https://www.upi.com/Top_News/US/2024/07/14/thomas-matthew-crooks-identified-trump-shooter/7311720966008"
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentence": "Using an AR-15\u2013style rifle which his father had bought legally in 2013 and that was legally transferred to him in 2023,   Thomas shot Trump and injured his upper right ear  and also shot three adult male audience members;  one of them, 50-year-old Corey Comperatore, was killed",
          "refs": [
            "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6tReC8aNS0A",
            "https://abcnews.go.com/US/local-swat-snipers-trump-rally-gunman-2-hours/story?id=112356606",
            "https://apnews.com/article/fbi-trump-assassination-attempt-shooting-f1ff0a636f3e2e1a28762c400852167e",
            "https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/nation/2024/07/29/trump-assassination-attempt-shooting-new-details/74586581007/",
            "https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/americas/us-politics/thomas-matthew-crooks-donald-trump-pennsylvania-shooting-b2579477.html",
            "https://www.bbc.com/news/articles/c98qnvn8dzeo"
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentence": "Crooks was then killed by a member of the Secret Service Counter Sniper Team",
          "refs": [
            "https://www.cnn.com/politics/live-news/election-biden-trump-07-13-24/index.html"
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentence": "Bomb-making materials were found inside his vehicle and at his home, and a remote detonator was found on his body",
          "refs": [
            "https://www.nytimes.com/live/2024/07/13/us/biden-trump-election",
            "https://www.cbsnews.com/news/trump-rally-shooter-death-attendee-butler-county-da/"
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentence": "The FBI identified him as the shooter on July 14",
          "refs": [
            "https://www.secretservice.gov/newsroom/releases/2024/07/statement-us-secret-service-director-kimberly-cheatle"
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentence": "As of August\u00a02024 [update], an investigation by the FBI was described to have at that time been underway",
          "refs": []
        },
        {
          "sentence": "Crooks's motivation remains unknown",
          "refs": []
        }
