            "https://www.nytimes.com/2024/07/14/us/politics/trump-gunman-thomas-crooks.html"
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentence": "According to the Progressive Turnout Project, he made the donation in response to an email about \"tuning into\" the inauguration",
          "refs": [
            "https://triblive.com/local/awards-and-recognition-program-honors-bethel-park-graduates/"
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentence": "He unsubscribed from the group's mailing list in 2022",
          "refs": []
        },
        {
